comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-30T19:37:11.721Z",codex-audit,"Duplicate check before create: pm context --limit 10 showed no active items; pm search 'manual audit sdk calendar telemetry dogfood extensibility' returned only closed prior audits including pm-wg1d and pm-mb4n; pm list-open/list-in-progress both returned 0. Net-new scope is required for the 2026-04-30 latest-build audit."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-30T19:37:11.721Z",codex-audit,Use real repository pm data only for audit tracking; all CLI dogfood project data must run in temporary PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH sandboxes.
close_reason: Superseded by pm-2eb3 (2026-05-01 Full PM CLI Dogfood Audit v2) which covers the latest 2026.5.1-2 build comprehensively
body: "Audit scope: dogfood the latest pm CLI in isolated temporary projects, inspect SDK and extension ergonomics, exercise calendar and project-management workflows, verify telemetry surfaces, document findings, and remediate issues discovered during the audit."
